"Saya kira itu
bukan kecelakaan."

00:20:49.120 --> 00:20:50.760 line:20%
"Apakah Anda mencurigai seseorang?"

00:20:50.960 --> 00:20:52.200 line:20%
'Saya mencurigai Atharva.'

00:20:52.640 --> 00:20:54.160 line:20%
'Ketika Dhairya
jatuh dari teras'

00:20:54.720 --> 00:20:56.040 line:20%
'hanya Atharva yang ada di sana.'

00:20:56.120 --> 00:20:57.520 line:20%
"Aku pergi ke teras
mencari Chini."

00:20:57.680 --> 00:20:59.640 line:20%
'Kamu mengancam
Dhairya berkali-kali.'

00:20:59.920 --> 00:21:03.000 line:20%
'Selama upacara pacar Anda
mengancam akan membunuhnya.'

00:21:03.040 --> 00:21:04.640 line:20%
'Orang-orang akan mengatakan
apa saja saat mereka marah.'

00:21:04.720 --> 00:21:06.480 line:20%
'Dan mereka akan
melakukan apa saja, Atharva.'

00:21:07.320 --> 00:21:09.800 line:20%
'Inspektur, saya curiga Atharva.
Tolong tangkap dia.'